2048 x 2048
30 second loop

Torn paper elements are placed by hand in a sequence of intentional compositions, then digitally layered with outputs from a custom machine learning model to introduce random interactions and fluid motion. 

Intimate fragments of familiar typographic forms vibrate untethered from language, expressing emotions where there are no words and there is no story.
